    <item>
      <title>Carpentry</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/infovault/skills/carpentry/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:47:31 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/infovault/skills/carpentry/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;To craft or repair something with carpentry you will need to use one of the carpentry tools: Saw, Dovetail saw, Draw knife, Froe, Inshave, Scorp, Jointing plane, Moulding plane, Smoothing plane or Hammer.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Using a carpentry tool on wood equipment near an anvil will try to repair it, higher carpentry and arms lore will increase your chance of repairing the item.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To craft items with multiple materials you will need to use your carpentry tool on the secondary material first and then the logs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
